data.description:
NO SECTION 8 VOUCHERS ACCEPTED!!

FURNISHED OR UNFURNISHED
Beautiful 3 bedroom, 2.5 bath townhouse within gate community!!
Approximately 2.5 miles off of cascade road and 285. Close to Downtown, Marietta, Airport

Cute and clean end unit 3 bedroom townhouse. Assigned parking. Gated community. All appliances in kitchen; large great room with fireplace. kitchen bar and separate dinning room. w/d upstairs. Lawn maintenance. 2nd and 3rd bedroom share jack and jill bathroom. No sign. No section 8.

Updated appliances (washer, dryer,refrigerator,dishwasher,oven microwave) included
Hard wood floors in kitchen, Granite Counter Tops, Marble Back Splash
Bay window in kitchen ,loft work space upstairs!!
Small, Gated community

$50 non refundable application fee
Credit check and background check required
First months rent and $1000 deposit required at signing of lease
